    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>// WIP</p><h2 id="Relevant-Software"><a href="#Relevant-Software" class="headerlink" title="Relevant Software"></a>Relevant Software</h2><ul><li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a></li><li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://obsidian.md/">Obsidian</a></li></ul><h2 id="How-to"><a href="#How-to" class="headerlink" title="How-to"></a>How-to</h2><h3 id="Initialize-a-Hexo-Project"><a href="#Initialize-a-Hexo-Project" class="headerlink" title="Initialize a Hexo Project"></a>Initialize a Hexo Project</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init my-blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><figcaption><span>_config.yml</span></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">marked:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">prependRoot:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="Open-the-Hexo-Source-folder-in-Obsidian"><a href="#Open-the-Hexo-Source-folder-in-Obsidian" class="headerlink" title="Open the Hexo Source folder in Obsidian."></a>Open the Hexo Source folder in Obsidian.</h3><p>To open the vault in Obsidian, go to File &gt; Open Vaultâ€¦</p><p><img src="/assets/attachments/obsidian-open-vault.png" alt="Obsidian Open Vault"></p><p>Select the <code>source</code> folder in the Hexo project to open it as the vault.</p><p><img src="/assets/attachments/Pasted%20image%2020230327234305.png"></p><p>Next, go to Obsidian &gt; Settings &gt; Files &amp; Links</p><ul><li>Set <code>Default location for new notes</code> = <code>In the folder specified below</code></li><li>Set <code>Folder to create new notes in</code> = <code>_posts</code></li><li>Set <code>New link format</code> = <code>Absolute path in vault</code></li><li>Disable the <code>Use [[Wikilinks]]</code> option.</li><li>Set <code>Default location for new attachements</code> = <code>In the folder specified below</code></li><li>Set <code>Attachment folder path</code> = <code>assets/attachments</code></li></ul><p><img src="/assets/attachments/Pasted%20image%2020230327234337.png"> <img src="/assets/attachments/Pasted%20image%2020230327234353.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
